    <intervention_name>Amlodipine</intervention_name>
    <description>Usual adult dosage is 2.5-5 mg of amlodipine given orally as a single daily dose. Dosage should be adjusted depending on the patient's symptoms. The dose can be raised up to 10 mg once daily for patients who show inadequate response.</description>
